description:
2022’s hit action RPG Elden Ring took the Lands Between by storm when it first launched, and its new DLC, Shadow of the Erdtree, promises to capture everyone’s attention once again. But hey—2022 was kind of a while ago, and you might be feeling just a little bit maidenless. Never fear—we’re here to show you the quickest way to get prepped for the Elden Ring DLC.

#gaming #eldenring #gamespot
title: Quickest Ways to Get Ready For Elden Ring Shadow of the Erdtree DLC
